readable.content: A girl in a gray shirt and brown hair relaxes on the lawn as dogs bound around her . A woman sitting next to her purse watching dogs at the park . A young woman sits crosslegged beside her purse on the grass among a crowd of dogs . There are several dogs in the field where the girl with the ponytail is sitting down . Woman sitting in the grass with many dogs around her .
